14
00:01:22,780 --> 00:01:24,379
Summer Market?

15
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:25,579
Yes.

16
00:01:25,580 --> 00:01:28,579
Rang Rang said there will be a market at Haiyue Square tomorrow.

17
00:01:28,580 --> 00:01:30,740
He said he wanted to go together.

18
00:01:30,740 --> 00:01:34,159
What do you think of confessing to him using this opportunity?

19
00:01:34,159 --> 00:01:35,059
Is it proper?

20
