83
00:04:56,580 --> 00:04:57,699
 Step two. 

84
00:04:57,700 --> 00:04:59,779
 Create physical contact opportunities. 

85
00:04:59,780 --> 00:05:03,459
 For example, you can accidentally touch his arm 

86
00:05:03,460 --> 00:05:06,139
 or fall into his embrace. 

87
00:05:06,140 --> 00:05:09,680
 Then, you will feel your heart racing. 

88
00:05:19,980 --> 00:05:21,339
That was close, Rang Rang.

89
00:05:21,340 --> 00:05:23,280
I'm glad you are around.

90
00:05:31,940 --> 00:05:33,880
Are you all right?

91
00:05:35,260 --> 00:05:37,619
How... How?

92
00:05:37,620 --> 00:05:39,499
Thankfully, I was quick to react.

93
00:05:39,500 --> 00:05:41,339
Look how skinny you are.

94
00:05:41,340 --> 00:05:43,180
You'd have been badly hurt if you had fallen.

95
00:05:43,260 --> 00:05:44,620
Sorry.

96
00:05:50,580 --> 00:05:52,019
Are you all right?

97
00:05:52,020 --> 00:05:53,520
I'm fine.

98
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:56,460
Let's walk on the side.

99
00:05:56,460 --> 00:05:57,700
Okay.

100
00:06:02,900 --> 00:06:05,219
 The most important third step. 

101
00:06:05,220 --> 00:06:06,499
 Signaling. 

102
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:08,739
 A confession requires foreshadowing. 

103
00:06:08,740 --> 00:06:10,979
 You need to let him know what you think. 

104
00:06:10,980 --> 00:06:14,780
 Confessing after that increases your success rate. 

105
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,740
What's wrong?

106
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:29,360
Rang Rang. I've been very stressed recently.

107
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:33,139
My parents want me to get married before 30.

108
00:06:33,140 --> 00:06:35,139
That means I have to get engaged at 29

109
00:06:35,140 --> 00:06:36,939
and meet my partner's parents at 28.

110
00:06:36,940 --> 00:06:39,379
I think being in a relationship for ten years sounds about right.

111
00:06:39,380 --> 00:06:42,680
It means I'll need to start dating at 18.

112
00:06:44,460 --> 00:06:47,280
You'll be 19 in a few months.

113
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,640
Can you make it?

114
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:50,579
Well...

115
00:06:50,580 --> 00:06:55,040
I think I can accept being in a relationship for nine years.

116
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:04,420
Oh, Rang Rang.

117
00:07:04,420 --> 00:07:06,380
Are you an Aries?

118
00:07:06,900 --> 00:07:09,299
When I read the horoscope book yesterday,

119
00:07:09,300 --> 00:07:11,939
it said that Aries is a good match for Sagittarius.

120
00:07:11,940 --> 00:07:14,179
Coincidentally, I am a Sagittarius.

121
00:07:14,180 --> 00:07:16,179
I'm celebrating my birthday on the lunar calendar.

122
00:07:16,180 --> 00:07:18,140
If it's the normal calendar,

123
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:20,880
I'm a Pisces.

124
00:07:21,820 --> 00:07:25,140
I don't think the horoscope is accurate.

125
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:33,019
 If all of these don't work, 

126
00:07:33,020 --> 00:07:35,379
 you'll have to use your ultimate move. 

127
00:07:35,380 --> 00:07:37,979
 I have a distant relative who lost his job two days ago. 

128
00:07:37,980 --> 00:07:41,379
 He will be opening a tarot shop at the market today. 

129
00:07:41,380 --> 00:07:43,379
 I already told him about it. 

130
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:45,419
 Bring Zhang Lurang over. 

131
00:07:45,420 --> 00:07:47,980
 You will definitely succeed with his help. 

132
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,979
The horoscope is not accurate,

133
00:07:54,980 --> 00:07:58,699
but I know someone who is really good at tarot card reading.

134
00:07:58,700 --> 00:08:00,779
Since the fireworks won't start any sooner,

135
00:08:00,780 --> 00:08:01,979
let's go there and take a look first.

136
00:08:01,980 --> 00:08:03,179
Really good at it?

137
00:08:03,180 --> 00:08:05,400
That's right. He is very reliable.

138
00:08:08,620 --> 00:08:11,579
Coming to me is the right choice.

139
00:08:11,580 --> 00:08:14,819
I'm famous in my village for tarot card reading.

140
00:08:14,820 --> 00:08:17,099
Let's just talk about what happened last month.

141
00:08:17,100 --> 00:08:18,979
Erniu, who was living beside my house, had the flu.

142
00:08:18,980 --> 00:08:21,840
I told him he would recover within a week.

143
00:08:21,860 --> 00:08:23,520
Do you know what happened next?

144
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:26,139
He recovered in less than a week.

145
00:08:26,140 --> 00:08:29,739
Those who have seen my ability will always say

146
00:08:29,740 --> 00:08:31,520
I'm very accurate.

147
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:35,179
What is your name?

148
00:08:35,180 --> 00:08:37,280
My surname is Hao.

149
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:39,600
My name is Zhun.
 (T/N: It means "very accurate") 

150
00:08:47,340 --> 00:08:48,490
Okay then!

151
00:08:49,820 --> 00:08:52,779
Since we met here, it means we are fated.

152
00:08:52,780 --> 00:08:58,780
Why don't I simply take a look for you two?

153
00:08:59,780 --> 00:09:00,780
Here.

154
00:09:01,300 --> 00:09:04,300
Pick a card with your feeling.

155
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,200
This one?

156
00:09:09,540 --> 00:09:10,900
Oh.

157
00:09:10,900 --> 00:09:12,960
Oh, my!

158
00:09:12,980 --> 00:09:15,120
This is an amazing card.

159
00:09:15,740 --> 00:09:20,080
Looking at this card, I can see that you are a very lucky person.

160
00:09:20,140 --> 00:09:23,179
You will also bring your luck to the people around you,

161
00:09:23,180 --> 00:09:25,980
especially people who are close.

162
00:09:31,020 --> 00:09:39,099
Whoever becomes your boyfriend in the future must be very happy.

163
00:09:40,380 --> 00:09:43,540
Hey, pick a card.

164
00:09:43,540 --> 00:09:44,840
Oh.

165
00:09:46,180 --> 00:09:47,580
This one.

166
00:09:49,700 --> 00:09:50,920
This is amazing.

167
00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:52,659
It's great.

168
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:54,059
Let me tell you.

169
00:09:54,060 --> 00:09:59,539
From this card, I can see what your future girlfriend looks like.

170
00:10:03,140 --> 00:10:04,640
She...

171
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:09,640
She... I think she

172
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:13,340
has bangs and bright eyes, and she's wearing pink.

173
00:10:19,900 --> 00:10:24,200
Can you see what her name is?

174
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:27,480
Of course.

175
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:32,140
What is your name?

176
00:10:33,020 --> 00:10:37,640
Su Zaizai.

177
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:39,140
Louder. I can't hear you.

178
00:10:41,140 --> 00:10:45,080
Why are you looking at me? She couldn't be Su Zaizai, could she?

179
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:48,080
Yes! Her name is Su Zaizai!

180
00:10:50,420 --> 00:10:52,400
It's too obvious.

181
00:10:53,940 --> 00:10:55,720
I think it's okay.

182
00:10:58,440 --> 00:11:01,500
Whatever. I've tried my best. Just leave it to fate.

183
00:11:04,180 --> 00:11:05,520
Jiang Jia?

184
00:11:05,980 --> 00:11:07,419
Why are you here too?

185
00:11:07,420 --> 00:11:09,939
I promised to meet He Yu and the rest here.

186
00:11:09,940 --> 00:11:13,680
Brother Gu Ran, is this your friend?

187
00:11:13,680 --> 00:11:14,699
Oh.

188
00:11:14,700 --> 00:11:16,379
She is the daughter of my mother's colleague.

189
00:11:16,380 --> 00:11:19,200
They are eating around here, so I took her here.

190
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:21,360
We are childhood friends.

191
00:11:22,220 --> 00:11:23,560
We only got to know each other last year.

192
00:11:23,560 --> 00:11:26,440
We already know each other for so long?

193
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:32,719
Since you are Gu Ran's friend,

194
00:11:32,719 --> 00:11:35,299
do you know if he has anyone he likes?

195
00:11:35,300 --> 00:11:37,900
He wouldn't tell me even if I asked him.

196
00:11:37,900 --> 00:11:39,341
- He... 
 - I do.

197
00:11:39,341 --> 00:11:41,100
I have someone I like.

198
00:11:41,940 --> 00:11:44,040
The person I like is her.

199
00:11:45,260 --> 00:11:48,019
You can't simply say that.

200
00:11:48,020 --> 00:11:49,320
I didn't.

201
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:54,059
She might not be the most outstanding person.

202
00:11:54,060 --> 00:11:57,560
She likes to hop around singing out-of-tune songs.

203
00:11:57,580 --> 00:12:01,099
She'd be too sad to eat because of a bad ending in a novel.

204
00:12:01,100 --> 00:12:03,900
When she is angry, I can't even stand her.

205
00:12:03,900 --> 00:12:07,340
However, when she smiles,

206
00:12:07,340 --> 00:12:09,800
she is the only person I see.

207
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,459
I've made it clear to you.

208
00:12:17,460 --> 00:12:19,220
Can I go now?

209
00:12:41,740 --> 00:12:44,360
Did you reward me for using me as a shield?

210
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:47,500
That was an emergency.

211
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:49,360
Fine. What reward do you want?

212
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:51,040
I'll give it to you later.

213
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:52,760
I'm not that petty.

214
00:12:57,700 --> 00:12:59,619
My friend just helped me.

215
00:12:59,620 --> 00:13:02,000
Can you help patronize his business?

216
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,459
Your friend?

217
00:13:03,460 --> 00:13:04,520
Who is it? Where do you know him?

218
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:05,599
Do you know his details?

219
00:13:05,599 --> 00:13:07,440
A distant relative.

220
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:10,600
It's fine then.

221
00:13:14,560 --> 00:13:16,460
Let me see.

222
00:13:17,300 --> 00:13:18,900
That's...

223
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:24,000
Both of you have a deep fate.

224
00:13:24,980 --> 00:13:27,819
This card is the Lovers.

225
00:13:27,820 --> 00:13:29,619
It represents a choice in love.

226
00:13:29,620 --> 00:13:33,320
That means one of you is troubled by love.

227
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:35,859
Can you ever stop the nonsense? You even lied to me.

228
00:13:35,860 --> 00:13:36,979
No.

229
00:13:36,980 --> 00:13:37,939
Hey.

230
00:13:37,940 --> 00:13:41,099
Be honest with me. Did Jiang Jia bribe you?

231
00:13:41,100 --> 00:13:42,819
You're taking advantage of me.

232
00:13:42,820 --> 00:13:44,619
I'm the one who gets the short end of the stick.

233
00:13:44,620 --> 00:13:45,859
I can't see that.

234
00:13:45,860 --> 00:13:46,860
That's because you are blind.

235
00:13:46,861 --> 00:13:49,059
When I go to university, people will be queuing to pursue me.

236
00:13:49,060 --> 00:13:52,180
Can any one of them be compared to me?

237
00:14:00,820 --> 00:14:02,020
He Yu and the rest are here.

238
00:14:02,020 --> 00:14:03,560
I'm leaving.

239
00:14:05,260 --> 00:14:08,979
Hey, was what you said about fate true?

240
00:14:08,980 --> 00:14:12,380
Do you wish it's true or not?

241
00:14:15,060 --> 00:14:16,699
Enough. Forget it.

242
00:14:16,700 --> 00:14:18,620
I shouldn't have taken it so seriously.

243
00:14:18,620 --> 00:14:21,060
I wish you good business.

244
00:14:21,060 --> 00:14:23,100
Thank you.

245
00:14:23,100 --> 00:14:26,200
Why does it feel like he is cursing me?

246
00:14:29,260 --> 00:14:31,060
Really?

247
00:14:31,060 --> 00:14:34,120
What if he confesses to you?

248
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:36,259
I don't think I will accept it.

249
00:14:36,259 --> 00:14:37,140
What about you?

250
00:14:37,141 --> 00:14:40,460
What do you do if a good friend confesses to you?

251
00:14:43,020 --> 00:14:45,419
I won't date one of my good friends.

252
00:14:45,420 --> 00:14:47,899
I think it's not easy being friends.

253
00:14:47,900 --> 00:14:50,579
What if something happens after we start dating?

254
00:14:50,580 --> 00:14:52,379
It'll be awkward if we can't even be friends.

255
00:14:52,380 --> 00:14:54,600
Yes. You are right.

256
00:14:57,800 --> 00:14:59,260
Hey, Gu Ran.

257
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:01,219
What a coincidence.

258
00:15:01,220 --> 00:15:03,260
You can buy us ice cream.

259
00:15:04,180 --> 00:15:06,859
I'm only buying ice creams for Fu Yao and the rest.

260
00:15:06,860 --> 00:15:08,899
You just get lucky that you are with them.

261
00:15:08,900 --> 00:15:11,260
So petty.

262
00:15:16,660 --> 00:15:18,219
There are no clouds tonight.

263
00:15:18,220 --> 00:15:20,280
I'm sure the fireworks will be nice.

264
00:15:21,540 --> 00:15:23,960
There should be some time until the fireworks display.

265
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:25,779
Let's play a game.

266
00:15:25,780 --> 00:15:27,140
Sure.

267
00:15:27,140 --> 00:15:29,819
There's a game going viral on the internet.

268
00:15:29,820 --> 00:15:31,219
Let me give you a test.

269
00:15:31,220 --> 00:15:32,579
The rule is simple.

